# CHANAKYA Radar

- AI Deal Health Board — **not** a workflow or lender-stage board.
- Kanban **only** — no List / Table / Calendar.
- Columns fixed: On Track · Needs Attention · At Risk · Dormant · On Hold · Completed.
- Cards are **never** draggable; only CHANAKYA classification moves health.
- Column panes: fixed height + independent vertical scroll (no “+N More”).
- Cards show borrower, OPP#, product, amount, up to 3 active lenders + stage, CHANAKYA Says / Why? / Recommends / Confidence.
- Never show Rejected / Lost / Cancelled / Withdrawn / Closed lenders on cards.
